pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: header-badge
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 24, 160, 20]
    content:
      style: "$badge"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: FIXINTEL PRO

  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 60, 1000, 45]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><span style="color:$primary;">4 модуля</span>, которые работают уже сегодня</p>

  - elementId: title-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 110, 50, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: mod1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 140, 560, 240]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: mod1-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 140, 4, 240]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: mod1-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [84, 160, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:users"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: mod1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [136, 160, 300, 35]
    content:
      style: "$sectionTitle"
      fontSize: 22
      color: "$primary"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: CRM

  - elementId: mod1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [84, 210, 516, 150]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.55
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Клиенты, абонементы, продажи. Карточка с полной историей. Timeline событий. Группы и сегментация. Автоматические уведомления.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="color:$success;"><strong>Статус: готово к внедрению</strong></span></p>

  - elementId: mod2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 140, 580, 240]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: mod2-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 140, 4, 240]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: mod2-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [664, 160, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:key"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: mod2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [716, 160, 300, 35]
    content:
      style: "$sectionTitle"
      fontSize: 22
      color: "$accent"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Access Control

  - elementId: mod2-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [664, 210, 536, 150]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.55
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>QR/RFID, турникеты, шкафчики. Интеграция KERONG. Офлайн-режим. Журнал всех проходов. Автоблокировка при просрочке.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="color:$success;"><strong>Статус: готово к внедрению</strong></span></p>

  - elementId: mod3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 400, 560, 240]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$success"

  - elementId: mod3-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 400, 4, 240]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$success"

  - elementId: mod3-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [84, 420, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:wallet"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$success"

  - elementId: mod3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [136, 420, 300, 35]
    content:
      style: "$sectionTitle"
      fontSize: 22
      color: "$success"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Finance

  - elementId: mod3-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [84, 470, 516, 150]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.55
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Касса, платежи, чеки ОФД. 11 платёжных систем. Кассовые смены, Z-отчёты. Комплексные продажи. Бухгалтерия для налоговой.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="color:$success;"><strong>Статус: готово к внедрению</strong></span></p>

  - elementId: mod4-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 400, 580, 240]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$warning"

  - elementId: mod4-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 400, 4, 240]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$warning"

  - elementId: mod4-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [664, 420, 40, 40]
    iconName: "fas:door-open"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$warning"

  - elementId: mod4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [716, 420, 300, 35]
    content:
      style: "$sectionTitle"
      fontSize: 22
      color: "$warning"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Visits

  - elementId: mod4-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [664, 470, 536, 150]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.55
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Вход/выход за 0.5 сек. Активные посещения в RT. Статистика по часам и дням. Кто приходит, кто перестал. API для Face ID.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="color:$success;"><strong>Статус: готово к внедрению</strong></span></p>

  - elementId: bottom-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 690, 40, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1180, 688, 40, 20]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "04"